        <item>
            <title>ROG Strix SCAR 16 (2025)  开箱，超强打机效能 RTX 50 系列 GPU + 新散热系统 + 易拆盖换 SSD、RAM</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/rog-strix-scar-16-2025-g635/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rog-strix-scar-16-2025-g635</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/rog-strix-scar-16-2025-g635/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[科技达人]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 14:01:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG Strix SCAR 16 (2025) G635]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1298340</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p3">自从 NVIDIA 发布 RTX 50 系列之后，<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">电竞电脑</a>又推向另一层次。而每次新系列推出，好多人会选择不砌机，而选择一部顶尖<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">电竞手提电脑</a>，随时随地享受游戏乐趣，在创作应用实行上也大大增加效率。ROG 电竞电脑系列除了 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/rog-republic-of-gamers/filter?SubSeries=ROG-Flow">ROG Flow</a> 平板系列之外，还有以下小编介绍的全新推出 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 (2025) 超强<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打机电脑</a>。这部电竞电脑搭载 Intel® Core™ Ultra 处理器 ，它配备 Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX 处理器，更搭载全新 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 50 系列 GPU 独立显示卡，让玩家在使用 2.5K (2560 x 1600) 画质流畅打机之余，也可开启光线追踪等最新图形技术。电脑更在外型、散热、升级空间以及萤幕效能上全面提升，独特 AniMe Vision 灯效、键盘与机身围边的 RGB 灯效效果更型格，外在同内在，这部<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打机电脑</a>都为你带来全新世代的打机体验。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05271-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05305-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">搭载最新最强<b> RTX 50 </b>系列<b> GPU <span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></b>图形晶片<b>175W</b>超高瓦数输出</h2><p class="p3">在 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/deals/rog/">ROG 手提电脑</a>众多产品中，这部专为打机而设的顶尖产品 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 <a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">电竞手提电脑</a>搭载 Intel® Core™ Ultra 处理器可选择高达 Intel Core Ultra 9 275HX 处理器，以及最高搭载 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090 Laptop GPU，Strix SCAR 16 和 18 更配备最高 64GB DDR5-5600MHz 记忆体和 4TB PCIe Gen 4 SSD 超高速储存装置，可说是现时最强的电竞手提电脑。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa-694x308.png" alt="" width="694" height="308" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa-694x308.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/coreultraprocessorfa.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05288.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05262.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p3">对游戏玩家而言，<a href="https://www.asus.com/hk/laptops/for-gaming/all-series/">打机电脑</a>重点当然落在全新 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 50 系列图形处理器，而且在 Turbo 模式下 CPU 可达 55W、GPU 高达 175W 超高瓦数；根据用家需要，选择 Manual Mode 下 CPU 还可再多获得 20W，整部电脑功耗可突破 250W，为游戏、创作软件带来超强动力。高规格 GPU 能提供流畅且细致的画面，加上 NVIDIA DLSS 4（Multi Frame Generation）技术，在 3A 大作或高帧速电竞游戏中都毫不吃力。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05337.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲今次测试的主机内置 GeForce RTX 5080 Laptop 图形晶片</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05251.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">延续「跑车级」设计风格<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>标志屏幕面盖，用料上乘</h2><p class="p3">今年的 <a href="https://rog.asus.com/hk/">ROG</a> Strix SCAR 16 进一步升华了它的「跑车级」充满未来感的外型设计。电脑盖用上更多 LED 灯制造更形格的灯效；主机围边的 RGB 灯效都继续有升级，全部都用料上乘。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298384" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05318.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
