        <item>
            <title>【评测】小米 Pad 7 Pro 详细评测	靓仔轻薄机身外携方便 + 荧幕表现不俗 + 电量不算长</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/mi-pad7pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi-pad7pro-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/mi-pad7pro-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 13:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[pad]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pad 7 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299887</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米早前在 MWC，除了推出了全新的 15 Ultra 手机外，还推出了不少新品，全新的入门旗舰平板 Pad 7 Pro 就是其中一分子。回到香港，Edward 借得这部平板并试玩了数星期，现在就为大家分享一下详细的试用感受吧。</p><h2>小米 Pad 7 Pro 开箱直击</h2><p>在为大家分享小米最新推出的 Pad 7 Pro 平板的使用体验前，先让 Edward 为大家带来它的开箱直击吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299921" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02038.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是小米最新推出 Pad 7 Pro 平板的包装盒，采用全白色简约设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02045.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者测试的是蓝色版本，规格为 12GB RAM + 512GB 内存版本，属于最高阶的配置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02042.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02040.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包装盒上标明小米 Pad 7 Pro 采用了 HyperOS 2 作业系统，并支援 Dolby「全餐」，即同时支援 Dolby Vision 及 Dolby Atmos。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02047.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打开包装盒，就会见到 Pad 7 Pro 包装在纸质包装袋内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02049.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02052.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拿起平板就会见到底部有一个白色纸盒，内藏 USB-A to USB-C 数据电源线及说明书，值得留意的是它并未附送充电火牛。</p><h2>设计与上代相近手感亦似</h2><p>相比上代 Pad 6s Pro，今代小米 Pad 7 Pro 在设计上大致维持相同风格，机身同样是采用一体化金属物料制造，机面亦是一块屏占比甚高的荧幕，不过今代就加入了更多清新颜色，相比上代只设石墨灰一种商务感较重的颜色，今代除了灰色外，亦设有蓝色及绿色机身，Edward 手上的就是蓝色机款，配上金属质感，无论观感还是手感都算不错。另外，今代荧幕细了，但机身亦薄了及轻了，所以外携使用时手感十分不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02057.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者借得的是蓝色版本，外表上颇为漂亮，而机身就采用了一体化金属物料制造，十分硬净。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02081.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身采用平边圆角设计，感觉就像一块四圆角砖头。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02084.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02086.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过它的机身十分轻薄，厚度只有 6.18mm，而净机身重量亦仅 502.8g，以一部 11 吋荧幕平板来说外携方便性算高。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02123.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过由于机身颇横身，所以横向单手拿机，长时间仍会觉得较重。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02126.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果单手直向拿机，手感不但较舒服，用来浏览文件或网页亦会更自然及舒服一点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02060.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身设计方面，基本上与上代 Pad 6s Pro 差不多，机背右上角仍设有 5,000 万像素主摄镜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02094.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机面荧幕顶部中央位置亦设有 3,200 万像素自拍镜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02067.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02069.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按键方面，机身左侧顶部设有开关键，而机顶左侧就设有音量键。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02088.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而开关键亦有内建指纹辨识器，解锁装置十分方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc02073.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机身右侧就设有 USB-C 插槽。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299943" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202503241-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而介面方面，它采用了 HyperOS 2 介面，操作上与其他采用相同 OS 的小米手机或平板差不多。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
