            <title>中国盈通推出香味 RX 9070 显示卡，海洋花香两款可选、外媒：闻落似洗衣液</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/yestonrx-9070-xt-sakura-atlantis-oc/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=yestonrx-9070-xt-sakura-atlantis-oc</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/28/yestonrx-9070-xt-sakura-atlantis-oc/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 12:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AMD]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Radeon RX 9070]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299883</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>一般玩家通常关注显示卡评测的效能、散热、价钱等，不过最近盈通（Yeston）推出的新示卡就新增了一项评测点：香味。Yeston 推出全新 Radeon RX 9070 XT 显示卡，以融入香味功能的独特设计，为硬件市场带来新意。该系列包括 Sakura Atlantis 及 Sakura 两款，分别散发海洋与花香气息。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_55821"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bs1O21ibuKM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2></h2><h2>香味设计引人注目</h2><p>Yeston 在 Radeon RX 9070 XT 将香味模组置于散热风扇旁，随风扇转动释放气味。Sakura Atlantis 主打海洋气息，Sakura 则是花香。外媒 Gamers Nexus 测试显示，香味似汽车清新剂或洗衣液，因人而异。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327141208_0_5f3-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327141208_0_5f3-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250327141208_0_5f3.jpg 1000w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
